Package: sgs
Title: Simple GIS (in Spotfire)
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Carlos", "Lozano Ruiz", email = "litos81@outlook.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/litos81/sgs
BugReports: https://github.com/litos81/sgs/issues
Description: A set of functions to perform mainly the OSGB36/ETRS89
  transformation by using the Ordnance Survey's OSTN15 transformation model
  without any other package dependency. Additionally, it includes a few wrappers
  to functions from the sf package to make easier certain spatial operations in
  TIBCO Spotfire.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: sf, stats
Suggests: testthat, goodpractice
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
ByteCompile: yes
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Collate: 
    'common.R'
    'sgs.R'
    'sgs_bng.R'
    'sgs_ngr.R'
    'sgs_points.R'
    'sgs_polygons.R'
    'sgs_set_gcs.R'
    'sgs_sf.R'
    'sgs_wgs84.R'
    'sgs_transform.R'
